Compiling condition

OS's / PHP's version
MS-Windows: MS-Windows 8.1 / PHP 5.6.15, 7.0.5
Linux: CentOS 6.3 / PHP 5.3.3

Compiler
MS-Windows: Microsoft VisualStudio 2012 Express / Visual C 2012 (VC11)
(PHP 7.0.5 - Visual C 2015 (VC14))
Linux: gcc 4.4.7


More preparation

PHP
 * Copy 4 folders at {VC solution dir}/include_php_src from php source.
  - ext, main, TSRM, win32, Zend
   -> Not need files/dirs in ext dir except standard, also not need {src_root}/standard/tests dir
  - Copy file: {src_root}/win32/build/config.w32.h.in -> {src_root}/main/config.w32.h
 * Library from php binaries(need only a file -> dev/php5ts.lib)
  - {VC solution dir}/include_php_dev/php5ts.lib


